00:21:27,680 --> 00:21:29,320
because windows and windshields

558
00:21:29,320 --> 00:21:31,360
filter out the relevant wavelengths of light

559
00:21:31,360 --> 00:21:33,680
that you want to get directly onto your retina.

560
00:21:33,680 --> 00:21:35,800
Okay, so that's the reality of it.

561
00:21:35,800 --> 00:21:37,360
In addition, please don't feel

562
00:21:37,360 --> 00:21:39,120
that you have to look directly at the sun

