00:22:27,480 --> 00:22:29,620
But if you can only get morning sunlight

588
00:22:29,620 --> 00:22:31,160
by going out onto your balcony

589
00:22:31,160 --> 00:22:33,960
and your balcony doesn't face east, rather it faces west,

590
00:22:33,960 --> 00:22:36,320
you'll still get a lot of photons from the sun

591
00:22:36,320 --> 00:22:37,480
reaching your eyes there.

592
00:22:37,480 --> 00:22:41,960
But ideally you would find some way to look toward the sun

593
00:22:41,960 --> 00:22:43,020
first thing in the morning.

594
00:22:43,020 --> 00:22:45,180
I realized that with kids and work and other obligations,

595
00:22:45,180 --> 00:22:46,180
this can be challenging,

596
00:22:46,180 --> 00:22:49,580
but it is a challenge worth meeting.

597
00:22:49,580 --> 00:22:51,320
Meaning don't lose your job

598
00:22:51,320 --> 00:22:53,180
or forget to take care of your kids to do this,

599
00:22:53,180 --> 00:22:55,180
but you can bring your kids to do this.

