01:19:47,260 --> 01:19:49,620
But if you're wondering what this protocol is

2016
01:19:49,620 --> 01:19:51,240
that people did for five minutes a day

2017
01:19:51,240 --> 01:19:52,820
that allowed them to, by the way,

2018
01:19:52,820 --> 01:19:54,580
pervasively improve their mood.

2019
01:19:54,580 --> 01:19:55,740
So it wasn't just their mood

2020
01:19:55,740 --> 01:19:58,300
while they were doing this five minute a day protocol.

2021
01:19:58,300 --> 01:20:02,260
It was improvements in mood around the clock, essentially,

2022
01:20:02,260 --> 01:20:04,640
as well as improvements in other physiological metrics

2023
01:20:04,640 --> 01:20:07,640
and other aspects of those six core pillars.

2024
01:20:07,640 --> 01:20:11,560
It was that physiological sigh that we talked about earlier.

2025
01:20:11,560 --> 01:20:12,520
Although in this case,

2026
01:20:12,520 --> 01:20:15,160
we didn't have people do just one physiological sigh.

2027
01:20:15,160 --> 01:20:17,740
We had people set aside five minutes per day.

2028
01:20:17,740 --> 01:20:19,320
So set a timer for five minutes.

2029
01:20:19,320 --> 01:20:20,800
They could sit or lie down.

2030
01:20:21,800 --> 01:20:23,860
They could do it any time of day.

2031
01:20:23,860 --> 01:20:27,100
And we just had them repeat that physiological sigh

2032
01:20:27,100 --> 01:20:29,360
for a duration of five minutes total

2033
01:20:29,360 --> 01:20:32,440
so that they would do two inhales through the nose,

2034
01:20:32,440 --> 01:20:35,200
and then a full exhale to lungs empty through the mouth.

